  render_p(sec3, "In solar physics: L=11 alone captures 68% of solar variance (Schwabe cycle). In biology: the rosehip neuron (human-only, cortical layer 1) has a 288um dendritic arbor = eigenvalue classes. Function: inhibits feedback. The transcendental is the primary signal and the last protector.");
